a. 1:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115306\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115306)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115306)\">D&amp;C 104:5,8,10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107575\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107575)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107575)\">Dan. 9:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111516\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111516)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111516)\">Mosiah 2:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116935\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116935)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116935)\">Moses 7:62<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108526\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108526)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108526)\">Luke 13:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113791\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113791)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113791)\">D&amp;C 43:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115594\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115594)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115594)\">D&amp;C 109:59<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113186\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113186)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113186)\">D&amp;C 10:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115344\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115344)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115344)\">D&amp;C 105:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115711\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115711)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115711)\">D&amp;C 115:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107407\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107407)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107407)\">Jer. 33:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107738\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107738)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107738)\">Mal. 4:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109812\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109812)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109812)\">Eph. 4:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112460\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112460)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112460)\">Hel. 6:34<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113869\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113869)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113869)\">D&amp;C 45:58<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113989\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113989)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113989)\">D&amp;C 50:40<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112203\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112203)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112203)\">Alma 37:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112317\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112317)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112317)\">Alma 42:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>